<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Farem - Accès interdite</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Staatliches|Quicksand" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        html, body {
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            color: #bfbfbf;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        a {
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .background {
            height: 100vh;
            width: 100vw;
            background-image: url("/public/frontend/404.png");
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-size: cover;
            /*filter: grayscale(50%) brightness(50%);
            -webkit-filter: grayscale(50%) brightness(50%);*/
            filter: grayscale(30%) brightness(30%);
            -webkit-filter: grayscale(30%) brightness(30%);
        }
        .content-not-found {
            text-align: center;
            position: absolute;
            top: 30%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%) translateX(-50%);
        }
        .content-not-found h1 {
            font-family: Staatliches, sans-serif;
            font-size: 200px;
            z-index: -1;
            letter-spacing: 50px;
            color: white;
        }

        .number {
            display: inline-block;
            vertical-align: top;
            transform: rotate({{ random(80) - random(80) }}deg);
        }
        .number-1 {
            transform: rotate({{ random(80) - random(80) }}deg)
        }
        .number-2 {
            transform: rotate({{ random(80) - random(80) }}deg);
        }
        .number-3 {
            transform: rotate({{ random(80) - random(80) }}deg);
        }
        .action-404 {
            font-family: Quicksand, sans-serif;
            font-size: 25px;
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 20%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>


<body>
<div class="background">
</div>

<div class="content-not-found">
    <h1><span class="number number-1">4</span><span class="number number-2">0</span><span class="number number-3">3</span></h1>
</div>

<div class="action-404">
        <p>Hé là, qui va là ? Cette section vous est interdite.</p>
        <p style="width: 250px; margin: auto;"><a href="/">Passez par la case départ, et touchez 20.000 francs</a></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
